@user1:
Does `linguist` follow `[attr]` declarations in `.gitattributes`?  If so, it might be nicer to add `[attr]generated linguist-generated diff=generated`, and then we just need to tag the generated files with `generated` rather than the full `linguist-generated=true diff=generated`.  That also makes it just one place to change things if we later want to add another tag to generated files.

